---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const explainer = `
**AmicBridge is a private access desk for capital and opportunities.**

We connect private people who *have* money with people and projects that *need* it.

We never hold funds, move money, or guarantee any agreement.  
All transfers, contracts, and decisions happen directly between the people involved.

### Who AmicBridge is for
- People who want to deploy capital privately (loans, co-investment, private deals).  
- People who need funding for a project, property, or opportunity.  
- People who prefer discreet introductions and curated matches over public marketplaces.

### How it works
1. Tell us who you are and what you’re looking for.  
2. We look for a potential match inside our private network.  
3. When you want to speak directly with that person, you unlock their contact via a small fee.

AmicBridge is about **discreet connection**, not control.  
We stay out of the money. You stay in charge of every decision.
`;
---

<Layout title="AmicBridge – Private Capital Connections">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
      Private capital connections, on your terms.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl">
      AmicBridge gives you curated introductions between people with capital and people with serious opportunities.
      No public bidding, no platforms holding your money – just direct, private connections.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN EXPLAINER -->
  <section class="mb-10">
    <Markdown content={explainer} class="text-lg leading-relaxed" />
  </section>

  <!-- PRIMARY ACTIONS -->
  <section class="space-y-6 mb-14">
    <!-- Create Profile Button -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+want+to+create+a+profile+on+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-blue-400 hover:bg-blue-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-10 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block text-center shadow-lg"
    >
      Create My Profile via WhatsApp
    </a>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mt-4">
      <!-- Need Capital -->
      <a 
        href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+need+capital+through+AmicBridge"
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
      >
        I Need Capital
      </a>

      <!-- Have Capital -->
      <a 
        href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+have+capital+and+want+opportunities+via+AmicBridge"
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg block text-center shadow-lg"
      >
        I Have Capital to Deploy
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING & UNLOCK MODEL -->
  <section class="mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How you pay AmicBridge</h2>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      AmicBridge does not charge a percentage of your deal and never touches the money you move.
      You only pay us for **access and introductions**.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-1">
      <li>You first contact us on WhatsApp and describe your situation.</li>
      <li>We look for a match inside our private network.</li>
      <li>When you want to speak directly with that person, you pay a one-time unlock fee.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      Standard unlock fee: <strong>799 NOK per contact</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
      Payment is handled directly with AmicBridge (for example via Vipps to <strong>92928373</strong>).
      After payment is confirmed, we send you the direct contact details of the matching person or opportunity.
      All negotiations, agreements, and money transfers are strictly between you and the other party –
      AmicBridge never holds or manages client funds and does not guarantee any outcome.
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
